cu.explanation_en: GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_X2U changed from '192.168.70.135' to '10.0.0.1', which is in a different subnet and unreachable, causing X2-U interface routing failures and preventing proper CU-DU communication.
cu.explanation_zh: GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_X2U 从 '192.168.70.135' 更改为 '10.0.0.1'，该地址位于不同子网且不可达，导致 X2-U 接口路由失败，阻止正确的 CU-DU 通信。

du.explanation_en: Ta4 changed from [110, 180] to [0, 180], where 0 is below the valid range for timing advance, causing Tadv/T2a misalignment and front-haul synchronization failures.
du.explanation_zh: Ta4 从 [110, 180] 更改为 [0, 180]，其中 0 低于定时提前有效范围，导致 Tadv/T2a 错位和前传同步失败。
